title: Do it Over Again
itunes:title: Do it Over Again
description:
Episode 497 - Buddhism says that the only guarantee in life is suffering, but what if we could go back and relive some of our toughest moments in our lives and see them in a different light? There has been proof that there is massive benefit in doing that and in this episode I will talk about how that is done!
